> > > reprinted in UNIX Review 3(1) 28, 118--120, 122, (January 1985) [no
> > > DOI or URL yet found], and more recently, in Resonance 17(8) 810--816
> > > (August 2012) doi:10.1007/s12045-012-0091-y.
